<br>
Hehe, and if you think banded is expensive.... wait until you hit plate.  MQ blocks of ore are about 20 PP each... and the cheap molds are 6 PP, with the BP running about 22 (that's with Ally faction and a charisma of 140).  Not to mention leather paddings... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
