 Well, anyway I must again that you, Gorte for the book and all advice that I have gotten from Amerygn and Malinki and all others). <br>
 One last question to leave you with. Is it tru that if I keep a copy of basic blacksmihing in a visible spot in my inventory that it will improve my success rate?<br>
